    输入:
      repo_name             仓库名
      family                家族
      basic_facts           dict: {syscall_count, loc_files, loc_code, members,
                                   trap_handlers, makefile_targets, ...}
      module_results        list of {name, title_zh, summary, narrative, refs[],
                                     data_structures[], interfaces[],
                                     open_issues[], unimplemented}
      family_baseline       字符串, 描述本家族标准实现 (ArceOS / rCore-Tutorial 已知特性)
